{title: Song with Bridge}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Em]Shadows on the [Am]wall tonight
[C]Candle burning [D]low
[Em]Whispers in the [Am]hallway say
[C]Time to let it [D]go
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[G]Hold on, [D]hold on, [Em]don't give [C]in
[G]Hold on, [D]hold on, [C]try a[D]gain
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_bridge}
[Am]Maybe there's a [Em]reason why
[F]We keep [C]holding [G]on
[Am]Maybe there's a [Em]brighter day
[F]Waiting [G]just be[Am]yond
{end_of_bridge}

{start_of_chorus}
[G]Hold on, [D]hold on, [Em]don't give [C]in
[G]Hold on, [D]hold on, [C]try a[D]gain
{end_of_chorus}
